ata-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Ben-Plenge-622600f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Ben-Plenge-622600f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Ben-Plenge-622600f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Ben-Plenge-622600f.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Ben-Plenge-622600f.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Ben-Plenge-622600f.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Ben-Plenge-622600f.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Ben-Plenge-622600f.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-613687 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--aspect no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/01/Ben-Plenge-622600f.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Ben Plenge riding.\" title=\"Ben Plenge\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> Ben Plenge works with everyone from weekend warriors to World Cup pros. He’s handy on a bike himself too.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"></span></div>\n<hr><p>For more information on Ben and his training services, check out <a href=\"http://www.thestrengthfactory.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Strength Factory</a> or his social media pages on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-2XWzlgKLOPLS0IhghSlEw/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">YouTube</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/strengthfactory_coach/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Instagram</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mtbstrengthfactory/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Facebook</a>.</p>\n<p>Ben’s fitness programmes include a <a href=\"https://thestrengthfactory.uk/bodyweight-mtb-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bodyweight Strength Programme</a> and a <a href=\"https://thestrengthfactory.uk/complete-mtb-programme-trail-end-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Complete MTB Programme</a>.</p>\n<p>Otherwise, don’t forget to head to the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/bikeradar-podcast/\">BikeRadar Podcast</a> page to browse through our full archive of episodes. Thanks for listening!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/the-bikeradar-podcast/id1461106709\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--full\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% * (167 / 687));\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/US_UK_Apple_Podcasts_Listen_Badge_RGB-ba30c1b-2.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C73, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/US_UK_Apple_Podcasts_Listen_Badge_RGB-ba30c1b-2.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C146 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/US_UK_Apple_Podcasts_Listen_Badge_RGB-ba30c1b-2.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=